originalText.text: Amazing healer. I have seen Emily several times for pain and issues with my cycle. Its been 8 months now and Im having a regular cycle, which for me is unheard of since I suffer from PCOS. She also helped me with my knee pain. It's about 85 percent pain free at this point which means I can avoid surgery. I recommend her as the first line of defense to anyone wanting to avoid more invasive procedures or prescription medications which can ultimately wreck havoc on your body.
